<p>Smith, J. (2019). Overcoming the ‘tyranny of the urgent’: integrating gender into disease outbreak preparedness and response. Gender &amp; Development, 27(2), 355-369. </p>
<p>Wenham et al. (2020). COVID-19: the gendered impacts of the outbreak. The Lancet, 395(10227), 846-848. </p>
<p>World Bank. (2017). Domestic general government health expenditure (% of GDP) – India. World Health Organization Global Health Expenditure database. </p>
